1
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:18,920
Weren't you reluctant?

2
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:20,760
How come you agreed so quickly

3
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:22,360
once he was used to threaten you?

4
00:00:24,040 --> 00:00:24,840
I'll give you.

5
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:26,040
I'll give you all.

6
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:28,400
What you want is me,

7
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:29,240
isn't it?

8
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:43,680
Such a brave face to face death.

9
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:47,840
Are you planning to coax me,

10
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,520
deceive me,

11
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,640
and let your accomplice go?

12
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:52,960
and then die?

13
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:56,520
I'm right here.

14
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:57,720
Whatever you want,

15
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,680
I'll give it to you.

16
00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:03,560
What do you care about?

17
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:07,760
That I hate you,

18
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,920
or that I don't love you?

19
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:23,080
You're not even pretending anymore.

20
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,160
You don't even bother to lie to me.

21
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,920
Lie?

22
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,440
You've done so many evil things.

23
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,960
I've hated you for a long time.

24
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,240
How dare you

25
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,280
talk about lying to me?

26
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,840
You wouldn't

27
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,280
have fallen for me, would you?

28
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,360
What if I did?

29
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,600
Then what?

30
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,840
I'm just unlucky.

31
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,480
Your grandma is still with me.

32
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,440
If you leave,

33
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:43,840
what will happen to her?

34
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,320
What?

35
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,000
What do you mean?

36
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,000
I...

37
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,320
My grandmother is still alive?

38
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:56,760
I won't let you die.

39
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,320
You're not afraid of death at all.

40
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:03,440
Only by keeping you by my side

41
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:07,200
can I make your life a living hell.

42
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:30,880
Sun Xun.

43
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,200
Qi.

44
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,680
Why are you here?

45
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,880
IPCO is looking for Brother Fu everywhere.

46
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:57,920
But no one should know

47
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,320
this place for the time being.

48
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:00,840
You'd better

49
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,440
strengthen security.

50
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,480
I found...

51
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,280
Does Sister Yan love Brother Fu?

52
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,600
I don't know.

53
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:47,040
They have saved each other several times.

54
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:49,160
They are so close.

55
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,160
Is the relationship fake?

56
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,360
You should watch less TV.

57
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,760
Don't think too much.

58
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,520
Only I

59
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:00,200
feel it's real.

60
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,200
Ah.

61
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,360
By the way,

62
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,280
Brother Fu

63
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:05,080
in Chamber Two, right?

64
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,480
I need to tighten security over there.

65
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,120
Qi,

66
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,120
we've been working together for so long.

67
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,320
You should know

68
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,240
what you need to know.

69
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,240
We should go, Fu.

70
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,040
This car has a GPS tracker.

71
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,680
Drive it to a place you think is safe,

72
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,640
then abandon the car and run.

73
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,160
There are still a few bullets in the gun.

74
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,160
It's enough to save your life.

75
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,160
What do you mean?

76
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,680
What about you?

77
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,200
I can't leave yet.

78
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,280
I have to go back to Pang Jingfu.

79
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,360
Go back?

80
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,000
We finally escaped.

81
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,640
You want to go back?

82
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,040
Are you crazy?

83
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,360
My grandmother is still in his hands.

84
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,400
We'll find a way to save her.

85
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,240
But if Pang Jingfu doesn't see me now,

86
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,440
