87
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:02,920
No.

88
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,320
I can't watch you die.

89
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,080
You must come with me this time.

90
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,120
IPCO

91
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,200
will help us hide our identities,

92
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,520
give us a new place,

93
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,800
and let us start a new life.

94
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,960
He won't kill me.

95
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,640
But if we get caught now,

96
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,320
do you think you'll have a way out?

97
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:21,480
Senior Brother,

98
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:22,520
I believe in you.

99
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,440
You must have a way.

100
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,760
I'm waiting for you and your colleagues

101
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:28,240
to bring Pang Jingfu to justice.

102
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,120
The road he took

103
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,640
is a one-way road.

104
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:53,840
I

105
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,400
can never go back.

106
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,960
He ran away.

107
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:26,880
Hmm.

108
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,960
He's quite irresponsible.

109
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,160
Why didn't he take you with him?

110
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,440
My grandmother is in your hands.

111
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,600
Of course, I have to come back.

112
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,360
Pang Jingfu,

113
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,440
my body,

114
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,920
my heart,

115
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,600
what do you want from me?

116
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,280
I want you to compromise,

117
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,200
Be obedient.

118
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,120
Stay by my side.

119
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,720
Just like before.

120
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,080
I've been lying to you.

121
00:08:58,760 --> 00:08:59,640
Pretending to be cute,

122
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,360
pretending to be jealous,

123
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:02,280
pretending to be scared,

124
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,120
pretending to care.

125
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,560
It's all to catch you,

126
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,400
to investigate you.

127
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,520
Don't you know that already?

128
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,240
If you want to pretend,

129
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,360
to lie,

130
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:13,680
just go all the way.

131
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,400
Lying to you,

132
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,280
hating you,

133
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,720
all require energy.

134
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,560
I'm really out of energy.

135
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,040
What do you mean?

136
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,520
Don't do this.

137
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,760
Tian Yan.

138
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,320
don't do this to me.

139
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,560
Pang Jingfu,

140
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,360
are you

141
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,400
begging me?

142
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:20,200
Begging someone who's lied to you for so long?

143
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,320
I'm begging you

144
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:31,720
not to leave me.

145
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:34,920
Keep lying to me.

146
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,440
Pretend you care about me.

147
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,400
Pretend you can't live without me.

148
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,880
Even if it's fake, I'll accept it.

149
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:48,000
I'll stay by your side.

150
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,040
But

151
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,280
can you keep me here forever?

152
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,840
Why not?

153
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:57,040
I'm Pang Jingfu.

154
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:58,400
Or

155
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:02,760
