156
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,080
Pang Jingfu,

157
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:22,040
you are so pathetic.

158
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,240
Yes.

159
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:30,240
We

160
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,600
all joined the Silver Light Hall

161
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,120
through the recruitment system

162
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,080
of the Fengyue Villa.

163
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:35,600
That means

164
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:38,000
Ouyang Qing and Pang Jingfu colluded

165
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,360
to use you for drug experiments

166
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,960
and control you to

167
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:41,800
work over capacity

168
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:42,720
and beyond your energy.

169
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,320
Right?

170
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:44,600
No, no.

171
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:45,880
Boss Fu

172
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,760
doesn't know

173
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,200
anything about it.

174
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:51,040
We all signed a confidentiality agreement with Fengyue Villa.

175
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,640
If we reveal anything,

176
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:54,040
we have to pay a lot of money.

177
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,520
So when Boss Fu asked us,

178
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,840
we didn't dare to say anything.

179
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,600
Did Pang Jingfu participate?

180
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,000
Did he secretly

181
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,760
in secret?

182
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,600
Later,

183
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,040
several employees

184
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:08,520
were completely disabled.

185
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,840
It was Boss Fu

186
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:12,000
who sent them to a sanatorium in the south.

187
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,960
He also secretly transferred us

188
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,920
to other places.

189
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,480
He said it was

190
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,160
a secondment.

191
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,760
In fact,

192
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:20,200
he was just moving us

193
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,240
to a safe place.

194
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:22,920
So you mean

195
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,040
Pang Jingfu wasn't involved,

196
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,640
and he was secretly protecting you.

197
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:29,080
Boss Fu is a good person.

198
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,360
Yes.

199
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,120
Although people outside

200
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:30,920
are all afraid of him,

201
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,120
he is really good

202
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,320
to us workers.

203
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,720
So the surveillance in his secret room

204
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:36,680
is because

205
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:38,440
he's been looking for the truth.

206
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:39,520
But...

207
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,240
Tian Yan,

208
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,080
if you know all this,

209
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:44,760
will you have a harder time to kill him?

210
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:47,720
Ouyang Qing's

211
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:52,040
experiment log repeatedly mentioned the professor's opinions

212
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,120
and

213
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,640
adjustments according to the professor's latest plan.

214
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,440
Who is

215
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:58,560
this professor?

216
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,080
Tell me!

217
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,120
A...

218
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,960
A team of consultants.

219
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,680
We haven't worked with them for a long time.

220
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,240
I've given you a chance.

221
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:17,360
A guest professor

222
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:19,280
can decide the direction of the core experiment.

223
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:20,920
The upgrade of obedience water

224
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:21,960
is to change from ordinary control

225
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,200
to long-term mental destruction.

226
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,280
What's the benefit

227
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,200
for your Fengyue Villa?

228
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,440
I have nothing to say.

229
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,080
You can investigate as you like.

230
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:36,160
Ouyang Qing is not the final decision maker.

231
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,080
He has superiors.

232
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,720
We can't hurt Pang Jingfu now.

233
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,720
He is an important clue.

234
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,480
and might also be

235
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,280
a breakthrough.

236
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,080
You must be careful

237
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,480
undercover around him.

238
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:00,600
Got it.

239
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:03,720
By the way,

240
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,040
protect Tian Yan.

241
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:27,440
Fu.

242
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,040
You...

243
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,480
Go to my place.

244
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:32,440
Okay.

245
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,680
What do you need?

246
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:37,840
Water the flowers.

247
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:43,080
And check on Tianyan.

248
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:48,280
You're just too scared to go yourself.

249
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,320
Got a death wish?

250
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:51,520
Alright, alright.

251
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,520
Water the flowers?

252
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,200
Wait,

253
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,600
I need details.

254
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,880
You can't just water any flower.

255
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,200
What if the plant dies

256
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,160
from too much water?

257
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:00,720
You know...

258
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:08,960
Cactus.

259
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:09,840
Ah?

260
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,800
Where's the cactus at home?

261
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:13,280
Boss asked me to come and water it.

262
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:15,800
There's no cactus

263
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:17,160
in this room.

264
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,800
No cactus?

265
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:25,240
This...

266
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,360
Isn't this a cactus?

267
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:27,760
Ah.

268
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,280
As long as it's green, it's fine.

269
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:35,960
Sister Yan.

270
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,200
I think

271
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,160
you're heartless.

272
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:46,160
People have to be heartless.

273
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:48,120
If you're too sentimental,

274
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:50,800
you'll have a lot of troubles.

275
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:55,520
Fu has been through life and death alone.

276
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,880
and specially arranged two confidants to look after your grandmother.

277
00:15:57,880 --> 00:15:59,560
He is threatening me with my grandmother.

278
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:00,280
Threaten?

279
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:02,320
What traitor had a good ending?

280
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,320
Did he hurt you

281
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,480
or hurt your grandmother?

282
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,640
The threat you mentioned

283
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:07,880
is that he worries about you but dares not come back.

284
00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:09,720
Then let me pretend to water this cactus

285
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:11,560
like a fool.

286
00:16:15,520 --> 00:16:17,000
I can't possibly believe him.

287
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,520
You don't have to believe him,

288
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:21,680
but don't let him down, okay?

289
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,640
I wish he didn't care about you.

290
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:35,680
My Lord,

291
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:37,400
Sister Yan is fine.

292
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:38,800
She didn't hit the wall,

293
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:40,200
threaten to kill herself,

294
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:42,360
kneel, kowtow, cry,

295
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,600
or beg me to let her out.

296
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,160
